SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: Notino.cz offers home delivery, parcel shop delivery, and in-store pickup. PROVIDERS: Delivery partners include DPD, Balíkovna (Česká pošta), and Zásilkovna. PRICING: Prices range from 35 Kč for in-store pickup to 79 Kč for home delivery. Free shipping is available on selected products. The cash on delivery (COD) surcharge is 20 Kč. NOTABLE FEATURES: Special express and evening delivery services are available in Brno, Ostrava, and Prague for a fee of 89-99 Kč. A wide variety of parcel shop providers are available. WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is presented on a clear, dedicated page with prices for each option listed upfront. However, standard delivery timeframes are not specified, and there is no information regarding shipping for bulky or oversized items.
